1
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:21,760
This is Wang Xian!

2
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:26,200
What about Qi Feng?

3
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,800
There was never a Qi Feng.

4
00:00:32,620 --> 00:00:39,140
=The Tang Mist S1=

5
00:01:57,780 --> 00:01:59,780
=Episode 6=

6
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:00,720
Du Ruo.

7
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,760
Do you intend to confess

8
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,120
to your crimes?

9
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:06,680
What do you mean, Commissioner Di?

10
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,760
The "water ghost" killings

11
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:11,000
were just a cover
for a personal vendetta.

12
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:14,000
You used Qi Feng's fake death

13
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:17,000
to murder Wang Xian,
Cai, and the others.

14
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,280
Must I lay out

15
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,000
every single detail for you?

16
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:23,960
Commissioner Di,

17
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,480
where is your proof?

18
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:31,400
You flinched
when you saw the charred corpse.

19
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,800
That's when I first suspected you.

20
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,440
When I said Laifu had confessed

21
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,640
and implicated Wang Xian,

22
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,640
you showed absolutely no interest

23
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,840
in where he was.

24
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,560
Lady Du,

25
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:46,240
didn't you care what happened to him?

26
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,080
With you on the case,

27
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,600
he'd surely be caught.

28
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:52,360
Because you knew he was already dead.

29
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,920
Dead men pose no threat.

30
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:57,760
You lied about Qi Feng's height

31
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,840
but forgot about his foot size.

32
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,160
You stayed silent

33
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,040
because the man lying there

34
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,280
isn't Qi Feng at all.

35
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,600
It's Wang Xian.

36
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,040
You didn't know his size,

37
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:10,640
so you didn't dare answer.

38
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,760
This is pure speculation.

39
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:19,040
I only wish it were.

40
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:20,880
You claimed

41
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:23,720
you saw Qi Feng screaming in the flames.

42
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,440
But Laifu testified

43
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:27,640
that the man on the bed
didn't move an inch,

44
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,880
even while burning alive.

45
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,880
That's because

46
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:33,240
you had heavily drugged him.

47
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,760
We found the apothecary.

48
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,160
He confirmed

49
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:39,280
the knockout powder in his stomach

50
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,880
matches the exact batch you bought.

51
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,120
Bring in the witness.

52
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,520
Make way!

53
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,680
Look closely now.

54
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:52,640
Is this the lady who bought

55
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,000
the knockout powder from your shop?

56
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:57,080
Yes, it's her.
It's this lady right here.

57
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,280
How ruthless...

58
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,840
I completely misjudged her.

59
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,120
Commissioner Di sees through everything.

60
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,520
I plead guilty.

61
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,920
I can't believe I ever trusted her.

62
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,120
What a cold-hearted woman.

63
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,120
How could she do this?

64
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,800
Six months ago,

65
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,840
after Wang Xian
admitted to killing Qi Feng,

66
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,640
I began practicing
Qi Feng's handwriting.

67
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,520
On that day,

68
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:44,370
(Ruo, meet at Buxianxian in two days)
I used a forged letter

69
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,300
(From Qi Feng)
to trick Wang Xian

70
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:46,740
into plotting Qi Feng's murder.

71
00:04:46,740 --> 00:04:47,710
Impossible!

72
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,440
I knew how cowardly he was,

73
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:51,155
and that he wouldn't dare do it himself.

74
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:53,520
Once he hired his arsonists,

75
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,800
I played nice

76
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,760
and lured him to Buxianxian early.

77
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:01,800
I spiked his liquor

78
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,355
with a big dose of knockout powder,

79
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:06,440
and surrounded him with flints

80
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,280
to make absolutely sure he'd die.

81
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:13,920
Light it.

82
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,280
You do it.

83
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,320
You coward!

84
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,880
Don't you want to get paid?

85
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,680
Let's go.

86
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,280
Move!

87
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:24,920
Go!

88
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,960
But I never expected

89
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,440
that he would wake up.

90
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,320
Du Ruo...

91
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,360
How were you so certain

92
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,600
those two would set the fire?

93
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:50,640
I bribed the mystic Wang Xian hired

94
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:53,520
to plant a deep, unshakable belief

95
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,440
that Qi Feng was burned to death.

96
00:05:55,900 --> 00:05:56,810
No...

97
00:05:56,810 --> 00:05:58,160
He was burned to death.

98
00:05:58,320 --> 00:06:00,780
He was burned to death!

99
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,440
Since water couldn't drown him,

100
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:06,320
I'll burn him alive!

101
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,400
Your Honor!

102
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,920
She deserves to die!

103
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,560
- Yes, exactly!
- Yeah!

104
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,390
She must be executed!

105
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,720
Silence!

106
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:24,880
Execute her!

107
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,440
There's a reason for everything.

108
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,120
You risked your life to do all this.

109
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,960
What drove you to it?

110
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,120
Wang Xian...

111
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,600
murdered Qi Feng,

112
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,520
and then he violated me.

113
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:40,360
And because I refused to marry him,

114
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,880
he repeatedly brutalized me.

115
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,040
Look at you.

116
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:53,120
You're not as beautiful
when you're hurt.

117
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,040
This fair skin

118
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,080
belongs to me.

119
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:01,840
But when I think
about Qi Feng touching you,

120
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,960
it sickens me.

121
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,960
Did I hurt you?

122
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,320
Ruo...

123
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:12,200
I'm sorry.

124
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,760
I...

125
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:15,040
I didn't mean to.

126
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,400
Ruo,

127
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,240
I couldn't help myself.

128
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,040
Ruo...

129
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,520
You're mine now.

130
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,640
Forget about him.

131
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,120
Start over with me.

132
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,840
We can start over.

133
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:32,000
Why won't you speak to me?

134
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,000
Why won't you speak to me?

135
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,920
What a tragic story.

136
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:01,960
This fishing net...

137
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,480
I'm the water ghost.

138
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,640
She's the water ghost?

139
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,680
How is that even possible?

140
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,960
The Qi family shipwreck

141
00:08:14,466 --> 00:08:15,960
was orchestrated by the Wang family.

142
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,160
I ordered men to sabotage the ship.

143
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:20,130
I'm the one who killed him!

144
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:22,520
Anyone who harmed my Qi Feng

145
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,160
deserves to die!

146
00:08:33,160 --> 00:08:34,688
You two used to meet here in secret.

147
00:08:35,040 --> 00:08:36,840
Now it belongs to us.

148
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:50,280
- So that's the truth...
- I see now.

149
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,680
They deserved to die.

150
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,600
The Wang family had it coming!

151
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,320
Commissioner Di, to protect my dignity,

152
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,800
you allowed me
to clear the Qi family's name

153
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:06,240
in front of everyone.

154
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,960
I am deeply grateful.

155
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:12,960
Ruo!

156
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,800
Ruo!

157
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:17,400
Ruo!

158
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:19,680
Commissioner Di!

159
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:20,920
It wasn't her!

160
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:21,760
It wasn't Ruo!

161
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:22,120
Father!

162
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:22,760
It wasn't her!

163
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,400
Father!

164
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:25,240
I'm so sorry.

165
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,640
I really am the water ghost.

166
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,000
I am the water ghost.

167
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,120
Father...

168
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:38,120
This is my final farewell.

169
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,880
First, I thank you for raising me.

170
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,720
I'll repay your kindness
in the next life.

171
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:50,660
Second, I wish you

172
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:51,840
a life free of worries.

173
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,320
Do not tire yourself
for my sake anymore.

174
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:01,800
Third...

175
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,844
I've been an unfilial daughter.

176
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,720
Despite everything,

177
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,640
I have no regrets.

178
00:10:25,044 --> 00:10:27,311
(Ruanjiang County Bureau)
Thanks to Commissioner Di.

179
00:10:27,333 --> 00:10:28,920
Otherwise, the chaos here

180
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,680
would never have settled.

181
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,000
Now that the storm has passed,

182
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,920
Magistrate Cao,

183
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,480
you can finally get some sleep.

184
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:37,240
Indeed. Thanks to your brilliance,

185
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,160
I am

186
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,600
grateful to you, Commissioner Di.

187
00:10:39,755 --> 00:10:41,160
Thank you so much.

188
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,760
If you truly wish to thank me,

189
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,240
just give me a small boat

190
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:47,280
and a capable boatman

191
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,920
to see us on our way.

192
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,160
That's easily done.

193
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:51,360
I'll see to it personally.

194
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:52,360
Right away.

195
00:10:57,940 --> 00:11:00,460
(Memorial Tablet:
To My Late Son, Wang Xian)

196
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,880
Those officials

197
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,800
are only ever quick
when taking our money.

198
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,280
Xian...

199
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:13,880
I have

200
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:17,200
failed to keep you safe after all.

201
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,800
Scum like him deserved to die long ago!

202
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,320
Your daughter murdered my son!

203
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,200
I haven't settled that score with you,

204
00:11:24,400 --> 00:11:26,280
and yet you dare come here!

205
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:28,000
Wang Xian was worse than a beast!

206
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:28,840
He violated my Ruo.

207
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,320
He deserved to die!

208
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,280
And what about you?

209
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:33,480
You destroyed the Qi family

210
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:35,560
and ruined Ruo's future!

211
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,720
You deserve to die, too!

212
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:38,040
Nonsense!

213
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:40,080
The Qi family died in a shipwreck!

214
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:41,920
What does that
have to do with my family?

215
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,560
Wang Dingrong,

216
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:46,360
did you really think
no one would ever know?

217
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:49,400
The very day the Qi family's ship sank,

218
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,560
I knew it was you.

219
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,280
Father,

220
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,240
everything is taken care of.

221
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,680
Now, it's your turn.

222
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,680
Your leg

223
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,160
must be broken.

224
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,120
Xian...

225
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,800
Can't we

226
00:12:03,800 --> 00:12:05,280
just fake it?

227
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:06,120
Father,

228
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:07,720
brace yourself.

229
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,480
This is terrible!

230
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,840
My father broke his leg!

231
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:32,320
Somebody help!

232
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,960
My father broke his leg!

233
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:39,200
Qi trusted you.

234
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,120
Without him,

235
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:43,320
would you even
have a place at the Salt Bureau?

236
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:44,640
And you repay him

237
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:46,240
by biting the hand that fed you!

238
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,560
You raised a beast

239
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:50,080
like Wang Xian!

240
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:52,520
Xian was my only son.

241
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,080
Whatever he wanted,

242
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:54,920
I would give him.

243
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:56,880
And Ruo was my only daughter!

244
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,320
I'll make you spend eternity

245
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:01,160
atoning for what you did to her!

246
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:03,640
Stop!

247
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,720
Let me go!

248
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:12,040
Wang Dingrong must
answer for his past crimes.

249
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,480
You cannot kill him.

250
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,400
Today,

251
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:19,440
I went to the provincial office.

252
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,720
I found no record from years ago

253
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:25,080
of the Ministry of War
requisitioning salt.

254
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:28,360
When the Qi family's ship sank,

255
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,840
why wasn't it recorded?

256
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,440
After the Wang family took over,

257
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:33,840
this official salt
was never dispatched again.

258
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,160
Let me ask you.

259
00:13:35,488 --> 00:13:36,560
Was this shipment of salt

260
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:39,280
deliberately fabricated by you

261
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,600
just to harm the Qi family?

262
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,200
Wang Dingrong,

263
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:50,080
you and Wang Xian
conspired to commit murder.

264
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:52,480
You will be thrown into prison

265
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:54,040
to await your sentencing.

266
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:54,840
Take him away!

267
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,977
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

268
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:10,200
Du Ruo has confessed to all the crimes.

269
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:12,120
The main culprit,

270
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:13,440
Wang Xian, is dead.

271
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:16,040
Why must you go to such extremes,

272
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,800
even sacrificing your own life?

273
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:21,640
Did you kill Wang Dingrong

274
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:23,080
to take the fall for her?

275
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:25,960
Do you want everyone
in Ruanjiang County to know

276
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:28,240
that the Bureau
arrested the wrong person?

277
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:29,400
Or...

278
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:32,280
are you the real water ghost?

279
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:34,600
Commissioner Di,

280
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,520
do you have any proof?

281
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,800
Of course I don't.

282
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:41,080
Du Ruo is the water ghost.

283
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,400
The evidence is solid.

284
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:44,040
Her methods are clear.

285
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:46,120
Guards!

286
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,440
Put up a notice

287
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,000
and inform the people
of Ruanjiang County.

288
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:50,755
Commissioner Di!

289
00:14:50,844 --> 00:14:51,800
That is not the truth.

290
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,000
Not the truth!

291
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,640
What part of it isn't true?

292
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,560
Posing as the water ghost,

293
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:59,000
she used a hemp fishing net

294
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:01,240
to drag Sun Qi into the water

295
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,160
until he drowned.

296
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,920
As for Liu Shun and Jia Gui,

297
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:05,320
she waited until they were drunk,

298
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:07,240
trapped them in the net,

299
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:09,480
and sank them with heavy weights

300
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,760
until they drowned.

301
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:13,920
Commissioner Di,

302
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:15,440
Ruo is just a frail lady.

303
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:17,800
How could she drag large men like Sun Qi

304
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:19,240
into the water?

305
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,520
Then she must have had an accomplice.

306
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:23,520
I will get to the bottom of this.

307
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:25,480
Du Ruo

308
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:26,840
hated Wang Xian to the core

309
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:28,160
because of Qi Feng's death,

310
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:30,000
so she burned him alive,

311
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,760
and killed Cai to silence him.

312
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:33,600
To toy with an official

313
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:35,080
is an egregious crime.

314
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,160
It is unforgivable!

315
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:37,600
I'm the one who killed Wang Xian!

316
00:15:37,640 --> 00:15:38,960
I killed him!

317
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:42,840
Wang Xian

318
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,120
destroyed the Qi family,

319
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:45,160
and violated my Ruo.

320
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,920
He deserved to die!

321
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:49,640
I had long been plotting

322
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:51,640
how to tear that beast

323
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:54,120
into a million pieces!

324
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:55,440
You're lying.

325
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:58,840
If you knew the Wang family
murdered the Qi family,

326
00:15:58,920 --> 00:16:01,400
why would you
marry your daughter to Wang Xian?

327
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:04,320
Commissioner Di,

328
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:09,920
have you seen the scars
on Ruo's wrists?

329
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:13,880
I just wanted her to live.

330
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:16,920
After Qi Feng died,

331
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:20,440
Ruo suffered constant nightmares,
as if she had lost her soul.

332
00:16:20,560 --> 00:16:21,840
She tried to kill herself.

333
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:23,920
During that time,

334
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:27,080
Wang Xian visited her frequently.

335
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,200
Let it go, Ruo.

336
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,320
He never left her side.

337
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,000
Until a year ago,

338
00:16:31,520 --> 00:16:33,000
when Wang Xian came to propose.

339
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:36,840
To my surprise,
Ruo accepted with a smile.

340
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:39,520
Back then, I truly believed

341
00:16:39,520 --> 00:16:42,120
she was willing.

342
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:43,200
I figured

343
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:46,880
the feud was only
between the Wang and Qi families.

344
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:49,840
As long as Wang Xian
truly cared for Ruo,

345
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,880
marrying into the Wang family

346
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,600
would give her a comfortable life.

347
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:58,000
It was only six months ago
that I found out

348
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:59,280
that this beast

349
00:16:59,280 --> 00:17:02,360
was using my life to blackmail Ruo!

350
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,720
Remember?

351
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:10,720
Your face and neck cannot be bruised.

352
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:11,680
Not a scratch.

353
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,840
If your father comes to yell at me,

354
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:15,720
I'm afraid...

355
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:20,200
I won't be able to stop myself
from killing him too.

356
00:17:22,760 --> 00:17:25,320
Ruo had no other choice!

357
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:31,080
Six months ago,

358
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:32,280
Du Ruo learned

359
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:34,360
that Wang Xian killed Qi Feng.

360
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:35,880
That was also

361
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:37,400
when you found out everything.

362
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:40,160
You planned these murders

363
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:42,400
for six whole months.

364
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,520
Yes.

365
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:48,920
I caught Ruo
practicing Qi Feng's handwriting.

366
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:52,480
I knew she wanted to avenge him.

367
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:57,080
I couldn't bear
to see Ruo's hands stained with blood!

368
00:17:58,440 --> 00:18:00,440
So I became the water ghost
to do it for her.

369
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:09,800
I used Ruo's forged letter

370
00:18:09,800 --> 00:18:11,040
to lure Wang Xian.

371
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,320
Impossible!

372
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:14,360
Are you saying

373
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:16,920
you killed all of them?

374
00:18:17,320 --> 00:18:18,200
And Du Ruo

375
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,800
is taking the fall for you?

376
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:21,680
I really am the water ghost.

377
00:18:23,800 --> 00:18:25,080
I am the water ghost!

378
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,800
I killed them all by myself.

379
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,600
When Ruo found out
I was the water ghost,

380
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,680
she wanted to protect me.

381
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,640
That's why she made up the story

382
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:38,000
about Qi Feng being the water ghost.

383
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,040
Father...

384
00:18:40,040 --> 00:18:41,440
Qi Feng is the water ghost!

385
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:43,720
Qi Feng is the water ghost!

386
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:46,200
Killing Wang Xian for your daughter

387
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:47,960
is one thing.

388
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:49,480
But why murder

389
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:51,280
Sun Qi and the others?

390
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:52,720
Magistrate Cao,

391
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:55,840
if they hadn't murdered the Qi family

392
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:57,240
just for money,

393
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:59,800
none of this would have ever happened.

394
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:03,320
Whoever hurts my Ruo must die!

395
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,280
Then where is your proof?

396
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,640
In my study,

397
00:19:10,840 --> 00:19:12,440
there is a River Transport Order

398
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:14,040
that I wrote to Wang Dingrong.

399
00:19:19,266 --> 00:19:21,040
(River Transport Dispatch)
Is this the one?

400
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:23,960
Commissioner Di,

401
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,440
you knew all along.

402
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:50,800
Father...

403
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,480
Father?

404
00:19:54,600 --> 00:19:55,360
Father!

405
00:19:56,822 --> 00:19:57,520
Commissioner Di!

406
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,360
Commissioner Di!

407
00:19:58,360 --> 00:19:59,760
I did everything! I killed them!

408
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:00,920
My father is innocent!

409
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:01,760
Please let him go!

410
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:02,840
Ruo!

411
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,680
I've avenged the Qi family.

412
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,840
I also killed Wang Xian

413
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,822
to get justice for you.

414
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,360
It's been two years.

415
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,840
It's time to let go.

416
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:20,600
You need to start a new life.

417
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,560
That's not true, Commissioner Di!

418
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:24,760
It's not true!

419
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:25,680
I killed them!

420
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,000
Please let my father go!

421
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:27,680
Commissioner Di!

422
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:28,640
Ruo,

423
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:30,560
stop this!

424
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:33,280
Father!

425
00:20:34,560 --> 00:20:35,320
Commissioner Di.

426
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:42,440
I'm not leaving, Commissioner Di!

427
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:43,400
Commissioner Di!

428
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,520
Father, I'm not leaving!

429
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:44,880
Father!

430
00:20:45,120 --> 00:20:46,200
Commissioner Di!

431
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:48,040
I killed them!

432
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:49,720
Let my father go!

433
00:20:56,080 --> 00:20:58,040
The peach blossoms
at Buxianxian this year

434
00:20:58,040 --> 00:20:59,720
are exceptionally vibrant.

435
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,440
Yes.

436
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:06,560
Exceptionally vibrant.

437
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:12,960
(In this world,)

438
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,520
(the purest love)

439
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:16,080
(is a parent's love for their child.)

440
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:22,400
Commissioner Di,

441
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,520
forgive my ignorance,

442
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:25,880
but are we still arresting Du Ruo?

443
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:27,360
Why would we arrest her?

444
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:30,000
Because there are
no peach blossoms at Buxianxian.

445
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:32,040
They haven't bloomed yet.

446
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,640
Then why arrest her?

447
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:35,640
What do the blossoms
have to do with her?

448
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,960
Talk less, and read more.

449
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:40,200
Magistrate Cao.

450
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:46,080
Isn't the murderer

451
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:47,840
already in custody?

452
00:21:50,140 --> 00:21:51,780
(Ruanjiang County Bureau)

453
00:21:51,780 --> 00:21:55,660
♪Breaking the chains
forged by the mist♪

454
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,360
I understand.

455
00:21:57,360 --> 00:22:02,180
♪Praying she sees the sky once again♪

456
00:22:04,770 --> 00:22:08,750
♪She plucks
the shimmering waves to adorn her brow♪

457
00:22:09,110 --> 00:22:12,740
♪To attend this radiant display♪

458
00:22:13,320 --> 00:22:14,600
Qi...

459
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:18,680
I'm all alone now.

460
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,340
Ruo!

461
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:23,980
Ruo!

462
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:25,580
(Yanbo Ferry)

463
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:32,090
♪As she wished♪

464
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:35,480
Wait for my return.

465
00:22:36,120 --> 00:22:37,200
I will marry you!

466
00:22:40,840 --> 00:22:41,640
Qi...

467
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:46,600
I'm here to marry you.

468
00:23:02,040 --> 00:23:02,960
Am I beautiful?

469
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:03,960
You definitely are.

470
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:16,280
(The peach blossoms
at Buxianxian this year)

471
00:24:16,280 --> 00:24:18,120
(are exceptionally vibrant.)

472
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:19,760
(Yes.)

473
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,640
(Exceptionally vibrant.)

474
00:24:27,420 --> 00:24:29,900
(Ruanjiang County, Langzhou)

475
00:24:34,260 --> 00:24:37,460
(Wangnian County, Raozhou)

476
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:38,820
(Part 2: Red-Faced Guardian)

477
00:24:38,820 --> 00:24:44,640
♪Life is a dream,
a dream like chasing the wind♪

478
00:24:44,930 --> 00:24:50,150
♪Yet I am lost within it,
refusing to wake♪

479
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:51,320
Help!

480
00:24:51,320 --> 00:24:52,080
Someone's dead!

481
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:53,880
Troupe Master!

482
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:54,800
Someone's dead!

483
00:25:06,340 --> 00:25:07,460
(Preview of Next Episode)

484
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:16,480
It's her.

485
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:17,480
Why is it her?

486
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,360
Divine punishment.

487
00:25:18,360 --> 00:25:19,310
Must be divine punishment!

488
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:20,720
In the dead of winter,

489
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:21,840
she danced barefoot

490
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:23,360
endlessly

491
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:24,920
despite the frostbite on her feet.

492
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:27,280
It was as if her body wasn't her own.

493
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:33,240
It was as if

494
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:34,480
the Guardian

495
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:35,840
possessed Master's body.

496
00:25:40,991 --> 00:25:42,571
♪Night covers the long streets♪

497
00:25:43,651 --> 00:25:45,361
♪The city remains silent♪

498
00:25:46,751 --> 00:25:48,341
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

499
00:25:48,601 --> 00:25:50,841
♪Words still left unspoken♪

500
00:25:52,241 --> 00:25:53,881
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

501
00:25:55,011 --> 00:25:57,481
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

502
00:25:58,101 --> 00:25:59,581
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

503
00:25:59,581 --> 00:26:02,721
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

504
00:26:03,341 --> 00:26:05,261
♪Love is born from desire♪

505
00:26:05,951 --> 00:26:08,081
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

506
00:26:09,221 --> 00:26:10,881
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

507
00:26:10,881 --> 00:26:14,181
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

508
00:26:15,631 --> 00:26:16,951
♪Someone once warned me♪

509
00:26:16,951 --> 00:26:18,471
♪To stop upon this shore♪

510
00:26:18,471 --> 00:26:19,791
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

511
00:26:19,791 --> 00:26:21,281
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

512
00:26:21,281 --> 00:26:22,401
♪If one thought retreats♪

513
00:26:22,401 --> 00:26:23,701
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

514
00:26:23,701 --> 00:26:25,041
♪But in this world♪

515
00:26:25,041 --> 00:26:27,441
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

516
00:26:29,271 --> 00:26:32,081
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

517
00:26:32,081 --> 00:26:33,551
♪Still I walk ahead♪

518
00:26:33,781 --> 00:26:35,001
♪Let it pierce through♪

519
00:26:35,001 --> 00:26:39,741
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

520
00:26:39,741 --> 00:26:41,981
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

521
00:26:41,981 --> 00:26:43,381
♪Covering every heart♪

522
00:26:43,381 --> 00:26:44,571
♪How many people♪

523
00:26:44,831 --> 00:26:46,201
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

524
00:26:46,201 --> 00:26:48,411
♪Yet call it♪

525
00:26:48,611 --> 00:26:49,951
♪Fate?♪

526
00:26:50,311 --> 00:26:51,491
♪Life and death♪

527
00:26:51,491 --> 00:26:52,751
♪Balanced on a single line♪

528
00:26:53,101 --> 00:26:54,271
♪Light and shadow♪

529
00:26:54,271 --> 00:26:55,531
♪Hanging side by side♪

530
00:26:55,531 --> 00:26:57,011
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

531
00:26:57,011 --> 00:26:58,421
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

532
00:26:58,421 --> 00:26:59,961
♪In the end, it is only♪

533
00:26:59,961 --> 00:27:01,341
♪A single misguided thought♪

534
00:27:01,341 --> 00:27:02,901
♪If unveiling the truth♪

535
00:27:02,901 --> 00:27:04,241
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

536
00:27:04,241 --> 00:27:05,411
♪Then this answer♪

537
00:27:05,411 --> 00:27:06,771
♪Can it still remain true?♪

538
00:27:06,771 --> 00:27:08,171
♪When love and law♪

539
00:27:08,171 --> 00:27:09,651
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

540
00:27:09,651 --> 00:27:11,051
♪Which figure before me♪

541
00:27:11,051 --> 00:27:18,251
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

542
00:27:18,251 --> 00:27:20,981
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

543
00:27:20,981 --> 00:27:22,571
♪Still I walk ahead♪

544
00:27:22,571 --> 00:27:23,811
♪Not for fame or glory♪

545
00:27:23,811 --> 00:27:28,681
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

546
00:27:28,681 --> 00:27:30,491
♪Human nature is clouded♪

547
00:27:30,491 --> 00:27:32,211
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

548
00:27:32,211 --> 00:27:33,681
♪Though this world♪

549
00:27:33,681 --> 00:27:35,051
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

550
00:27:35,051 --> 00:27:37,301
♪There is still a light♪

551
00:27:37,301 --> 00:27:40,261
♪Worth pursuing♪

552
00:27:40,261 --> 00:27:42,081
♪Every case has its ending♪

553
00:27:42,081 --> 00:27:43,341
♪But night does not always fade♪

554
00:27:43,611 --> 00:27:44,991
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

555
00:27:44,991 --> 00:27:46,211
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

556
00:27:46,481 --> 00:27:47,561
♪If justice stands♪

557
00:27:47,561 --> 00:27:48,811
♪Without mercy beside it♪

558
00:27:48,811 --> 00:27:50,611
♪Then how is it♪

559
00:27:50,611 --> 00:28:00,171
♪Any different from a blade?♪

560
00:28:00,171 --> 00:28:03,361
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

561
00:28:03,361 --> 00:28:04,841
♪Still I walk ahead♪

562
00:28:04,841 --> 00:28:06,231
♪Even if the world♪

563
00:28:06,231 --> 00:28:10,961
♪Refuses to answer♪

564
00:28:10,961 --> 00:28:12,921
♪When every hidden truth♪

565
00:28:12,921 --> 00:28:14,631
♪Finally reveals itself♪

566
00:28:14,631 --> 00:28:15,991
♪I only wish♪

567
00:28:15,991 --> 00:28:17,471
♪To hold on♪

568
00:28:17,471 --> 00:28:22,211
♪Within the darkness♪

569
00:28:22,211 --> 00:28:24,211
♪To the heart♪

